this dir contains the script to fix warning ranges on an exisiting data fits file. 
it won't fix statistics part, but useful for fixing the plotting warning area.

Usage:

ck_and_dirty_limit_fix.py <fits file name> <yellow lower> < yellow upper> < red lower> <red upper> 
                          <start time of the fixing range> <stopping time of the fixing range> 


time is seconds from 1998.1.1
